&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-12 col-md-12&quot;&gt;&lt;img id=&quot;bor&quot; src=&quot;data/uploads/innerbanner4.jpg&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;col-sm-12 col-md-12&quot;&gt;
		&lt;h4&gt;Technological &amp;amp; Infrastructure Highlights&lt;/h4&gt;
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;1. Comprehensive gastro department with OPD, emergency and indoor services.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;2. Complete medical &amp;amp; surgical treatment of digestive system &amp;amp; liver disease &amp;amp; pancreatobiliary diseases&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;3. First time in region Bariatric Surgery unit for permanent weight loss.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;4. Dedicated modular OT for advance laparoscopic /minimal access surgeries.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;5. State of art Karl storz and Stryker HD - camera for advance laparoscopy.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;6. Ethicon endosurgery Harmonic scalpel &amp;amp; Erbe Vesselseal device.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;7. Endoscopy suite with Olympus k-170 series for upper Gastro Endoscopy and lower Gastro Colonoscopy - both diagnostic and therapeutic.&lt;/li&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;8. ERCP and all other advanced therapeutic endoscopic procedure with C arm Guidance.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
